BILL NO. 36-0042
Thirty-Sixth Legislature of the Virgin Islands
February 27, 2025
An Act amending title 33 Virgin Islands Code subtitle 3, chapter 118, section 3411 to increase
the maximum judgement amount for the award of damages against the Government of the
Virgin Islands
PROPOSED BY: Senator Alma Francis Heyliger
1 Be it enacted by the Legislature of the Virgin Islands:
2 SECTION 1. Title 33 Virgin Islands Code, subtitle 3, chapter 118, section 3411,
3 subsection (c) is amended by striking “$25,000” and inserting “$150,000”.
4 BILL SUMMARY
5 This bill amends title 33 Virgin Islands Code, subtitle 3, chapter 118, section 3411,
6 subsection (c) to increase the amount of money that a claimant can recover from the
7 Government of the Virgin Islands.
